Package: RankHistBins
Type: Package
Title: Analysis on bin numbers in rank histograms
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Claudio Heinrich
Maintainer: Claudio Heinrich <claudio.heinrich@nr.no>
Description: This package accompanies the paper 'On the number of 
    bins in a rank histogram'. In particular it provides tools to create
    histograms with any bin number from rank data and allows to compute 
    optimal bin numbers for any acceptance threshold, any size of test alpha,
    and any number of observations n (see paper for detail).
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
imports:
  devtools
  data.table
  ggplot2
  stats
